If it is successful it will return the value, otherwise, if an exception is thrown, it&#39;s caught and a new _[IllegalArgumentException](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/IllegalArgumentException.html)_ exception is thrown, with the input value as the _message_.

